<h1 id="why-tinkering">Why Tinkering?</h1>

<p>By tinkering with digital text, I mean engaging with text as a process involving analysis/decomposition and synthesis/recomposition. In line with the historical examples given in <a href="3">On Interconnection and the Boundary of Documents</a>, that means breaking a text into parts to create something new, based on an epistemological position about the notion of ideas as being interconnected.</p>
